@dsalt That was a Mesa issue and has been fixed a few days ago with the following patch [aco: Lower divergent bool phis iteratively](https://github.com/ValveSoftware/Proton/files/11749817/23.1.99-aco_eldenring_rt_fix.patch.txt)

You can apply that patch into your local tree or use mesa-git for the time being.

The game doesn't crash anymore and works fine (except for performance, but that's another topic) on my 6800XT.
